---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Mirisni potpisi - Priručnik za kreiranje prirodnih parfema | Fragrant Signatures" 
  description="Sveobuhvatan priručnik za kreiranje prirodnih parfema. Naučite tehnike parfumeristike, botaniku mirisnih biljaka i kreirajte vlastite mirisne potpise. 55,00 eura s dostavom."
  currentPath="/"
>
  <!-- Hero Section - Clean & Modern -->
  <section class="relative py-16 lg:py-24">
    <!-- Animated Background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-botanical-50 via-book-100 to-nature-50">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20width%3D%2260%22%20height%3D%2260%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2060%2060%22%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A//www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%3E%3Cg%20fill%3D%22none%22%20fill-rule%3D%22evenodd%22%3E%3Cg%20fill%3D%22%237D7FBC%22%20fill-opacity%3D%220.05%22%3E%3Ccircle%20cx%3D%2230%22%20cy%3D%2230%22%20r%3D%222%22/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E')] opacity-40"></div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Modern Header -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <!-- Left: Text Content -->
          <div class="text-left">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-botanical-100 text-botanical-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
              Prirodna parfemeristika
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-botanical-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
              Priručnik za kreiranje prirodnih parfema
            </h1>
            
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-botanical-600 mb-2">
              55,00 €
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm text-ink-600 mb-6">
              uključuje dostavu unutar Hrvatske
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-xl text-ink-800 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
              Otkrijte umjetnost prirodne parfemeristike sveobuhvatnim vodičem za kreiranje parfema.
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
              <a
                href="/edukacija/"
                class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-botanical-600 to-botanical-700 text-white rounded-xl font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
              >
                Edukacija
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                </svg>
              </a>
              <a
                href="/naruci/"
                class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-nature-600 to-nature-700 text-white rounded-xl font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
              >
                Naruči priručnik
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Right: Book Cover -->
          <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
            <div class="relative">
              <img 
                src="/images/Naslovnica-HR.jpg" 
                alt="Mirisni potpisi - Priručnik za kreiranje prirodnih parfema" 
                class="w-80 md:w-96 h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-2xl"
              />
              
              <!-- Badge -->
              <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-500 to-accent-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-2xl shadow-lg font-bold text-sm">
                Dostupno
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
    
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-botanical-800 mb-6">
          Zašto ovaj priručnik
        </h2>
        
        <!-- Quote Card -->
        <div class="bg-[#e8f0ff] rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-botanical-150 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
          <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-ink-800 italic leading-relaxed mb-6">
            "Kad jedno podučava, dvoje uči."
          </blockquote>
          <cite class="text-lg text-botanical-700 font-semibold">Robert Heinlein</cite>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Two Column Cards -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto mb-12">
          <!-- Left Card: About the Manual -->
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-xl border border-botanical-100">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-botanical-800 mb-6 text-center">
              O priručniku
            </h3>
            <div class="text-lg text-ink-800 leading-relaxed space-y-6 text-left">
              <p>
                Među osobama koje cijene prirodne mirise raste broj onih koji su odlučili prema vlastitim mirisnim preferencijama i zamislima sami sebi kreirati parfeme od prirodnih sastojaka. Ta scena je vrlo živahna, puna znatiželjnih, vrlo motiviranih i strastveno posvećenih ljudi.
              </p>
              
              <p>
                Za mene je, kad sam 2005. g. počela podučavati vještinu kreiranja prirodnih parfema, bilo ugodno iznenađenje da postoji toliki interes za to znanje. Kako bih što bolje odgovorila na očekivanja polaznika, htjela sam saznati što ljude motivira da prisustvuju toj edukaciji i kakvi su njeni konačni rezultati.
              </p>
              
              <p>
                Ovaj priručnik je nastao iz radnog materijala namijenjenog polaznicima edukacije Mirisni potpisi. Materijal je dodatno proširen detaljnim, korak-po-korak prikazima postupaka u svim fazama kreiranja prirodnog parfema.
              </p>
              
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 bg-gradient-to-r from-botanical-50 to-nature-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-accent-500">
                Nadam se da će vam priručnik uspješno poslužiti tijekom avanture otkrivanja i kreiranja vašeg mirisnog potpisa. Mirišite prirodno, osjećajte se dobro!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Right Card: Why Choose Natural Perfumes -->
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-xl border border-botanical-100">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-botanical-800 mb-6 text-center">
              Zašto odabrati prirodne parfeme?
            </h3>
            <div class="text-lg text-ink-800 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
              <p class="text-xl font-medium text-ink-800">
                U kojoj god fazi svoje cjeloživotne mirisne avanture se nalazili, trebate cijeniti ovu lijepo napisanu knjigu.
              </p>
              
              <p>
                Slobodankin pedantan pristup osigurava da budu uključeni svi aspekti prirodne parfimeristike – njezini korijeni, teorijske perspektive i praksa, uz istovremeno poticanje svjesnosti i kreativnosti.
              </p>
              
              <p>
                Priručnik o kreiranju parfema je jasan i inspirativan, prilagođava klasične metode raznim oblicima prirodnih parfema. Autoričino opsežno znanje, iskustvo, umijeće i strast blistaju na svakoj stranici.
              </p>
              
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink-800 bg-gradient-to-r from-botanical-50 to-nature-50 p-4 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-accent-500">
                Tour de force, Mirisni potpisi su mnogo više od vodiča ili priručnika – knjiga je predodređena da postane klasičan i važan tekst o prirodnoj i botaničkoj parfimeristici.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Author Quote -->
            <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-botanical-200">
              <div class="text-right">
                <p class="text-ink-800 italic text-lg font-medium">
                  Jennifer Peace Rhind
                </p>
                <p class="text-ink-600 text-sm">
                  konzultantica za eterična ulja, autorica knjiga o eteričnim uljima i njihovoj primjeni
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Feature 1 - Uvod -->
        <a href="/uvod/" class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-botanical-50 to-nature-50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-botanical-100 block">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-100 to-nature-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-botanical-800 mb-4">Uvod</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
              Kompletan uvod u svijet prirodnih parfema i pregled svih 15 poglavlja priručnika
            </p>
          </div>
        </a>
        
        <!-- Feature 2 - Sadržaj priručnika -->
        <a href="/o-prirucniku/" class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-nature-50 to-botanical-50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-botanical-100 block">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-botanical-100 to-accent-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-botanical-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-botanical-800 mb-4">Sadržaj priručnika</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
              Kompletan pregled svih 15 poglavlja priručnika za kreiranje prirodnih parfema
            </p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Feature 3 - Recenzije -->
        <a href="/recenzije/" class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-botanical-50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-botanical-100 block">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-nature-100 to-botanical-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-nature-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-botanical-800 mb-4">Recenzije</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
              Pročitajte recenzije stručnjaka o Fragrant Signatures priručniku
            </p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Feature 4 - Wallpapers -->
        <a href="/pozadine/" class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-nature-50 to-accent-50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-botanical-100 block">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-nature-100 to-accent-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-nature-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-botanical-800 mb-4">Pozadine</h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
              Preuzmite besplatne pozadine za desktop i mobilne uređaje s botaničkim motivima
            </p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Author Preview Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-botanical-50 to-nature-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-botanical-800 mb-6">
              Upoznajte autoricu
            </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-botanical-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
		  Slobodanka Poštić, poštovateljica prirode i profesorica, autorica je nekoliko knjiga o aromaterapiji.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/o-autorici/"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-nature-600 to-nature-700 text-white rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            Saznajte više
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="relative rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="/images/slobodanka.jpg"
              alt="Slobodanka Poštić - autorica Fragrant Signatures"
              loading="lazy"
              class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Newsletter/Contact Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-center relative z-10">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-botanical-50 to-nature-50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-12 shadow-2xl border border-botanical-100">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-botanical-800 mb-6">
          Pridružite se zajednici
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-ink-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Budite dio zajednice ljubitelja prirodnih parfema i saznajte najnovije vijesti o edukacijama i događanjima
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
          <a
            href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/289513248317640"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-botanical-600 to-botanical-700 text-white rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/>
            </svg>
            Facebook grupa
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/fragrant.signatures"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-nature-600 to-nature-700 text-white rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 transform hover:scale-105 hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"/>
            </svg>
            Instagram
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

